0:

”Alexa, ask my local bikeshare how full is station 31,005”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my local bikeshare
des:
v1.0

This skill allows the user to check the status of a specific bikeshare station. It will provide the number of bikes available to check out as well as the number of open docks to check a bike in.

Bike share station number is found via map: https://secure.capitalbikeshare.com/map/

This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Motivate International, Inc.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
